data.description: The attendant gated community of Willow Ridge has resort-style living in the heart of Signal Hill. The grand entrance gates welcome you! The grounds are lush with over 200 trees nestled into grassy knolls. A short drive takes you past the expansive seasonally-heated swimming pool and spa area in prime condition. The clubhouse is perched above the pool area and can be reserved for events! Also included are the gym and billiards room. Adjacent are two competition-level tennis courts. Located at the very top of the complex Unit 206 overlooks the tennis courts with tree-top views. This end-unit is a large approximately 1,143 square feet with two bedrooms and two bathrooms. The large primary features a corner window with tree-top views and the mountains in the distance. There are two large hall closets and an attached 3/4 bathroom. There is also a large bathroom in the hallway. Plantation shutters are in both bedrooms. The kitchen overlooks the beautiful courtyard with treetop views and has a pass-through space to the dining area. The kitchen lighting system has recessed can lighting and crown molding. Appliances are included! The living room is open and has lots of natural light. There are two sliding doors to the big balcony! More treetop views and the mountains beyond. Enjoy a cozy evening in front of the gas fireplace! This unit has pure privacy with nature and tranquility. Included parking features two under-building parking spaces both with storage cabinets! The laundry is inside the home and the washer and dryer are included. The HOA is pet friendly! The complex is well-maintained and a fabulous place to call home.
